						               													<description>There is a great demand for fruit bags!&amp;#10;To earn points you have to fill the bags with as much weight as possible.&amp;#10;To achieve this goal you can mix the content and even add some stone.&amp;#10;It is a game where you can be honest or deceive others at the risk of being found out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player has different fruit cards in his hand. These fruits have a weight from 1 to 10, there are also stones that weigh 11.&amp;#10;In the first phase, all players secretly use their fruit cards at the same time to fill the different bags on the table with the greatest possible weight.&amp;#10;In the second phase, using rings, all players can distrust the fruits that other players have placed.&amp;#10;In the third phase, the cards are revealed and it is defined who takes the bag according to what they put.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The bags add points at the end of the game. The more bags of the same type, the more points that player will get.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
